12.     OTHER RECORDS AND CURIOSITIES

*  Matches without receiving goals:   307
*  Matches without converting goals:  156
*  Matches with record of victories:  134 (GD  3+)
*  Matches with record of defeats:     26 (GD -3+)

*  Best unbeaten serie at home:        39 [29-10-0] matches (30-04-1997 / 11-10-2008)
*  Best unbeaten serie at away:        14 [ 7- 7-0] matches (03-05-1990 / 08-08-1993)
*  Best unbeaten serie at neutral:     26 [23- 3-0] matches (12-02-1941 / 01-02-1956)

13.     ABBREVIATIONS AND NOTES

ABBREVIATIONS

CW: Cups Won                GF: Goals For (scored)
MN: Match Number            GA: Goals Against (conceded)
MP: Matches Played          GD: Goal Difference
MW: Matches Won             GS: Goals Scored
MD: Matches Drawn          PTS: Points
ML: Matches Lost           ANT: Argentina National Team
M : Matches                FNT: Foreign National Team
C1: Cities                  NT: National Teams
C2: Countries               Nº: Number



NOTES

1. Points calculated on the basis of 2-1-0 (MW-MD-ML).
2. Matches defined by penalties are counted as draws. Exception: match number 488.
   The penalty shootout is not counted as goals.
3. In the results of the matches, Argentina is mentioned first.
4. The date format is dd/mm/yyyy.

